The June 2026 meeting of LRUG will be on *Monday the 8th of June*,
from _6:00pm_ to _8:00pm_ (meeting starts at _6:30pm_).  The venue this
month is provided by [Unboxed](https://unboxed.co/) and is in [their
offices][unboxed-venue], on Commercial Street, near Liverpool Street,
Aldgate East, and Shoreditch High Street stations.  [Full venue and
registration details are given below](#june26registration).

